---
description: Config management rules for Hyprdots
globs: 
---
- Never auto-commit. Always ask before committing.
- Config files must be stored inside the hyprdots repo directory, then symlinked to their target location (e.g. `~/.config/hyprdots/kitty/kitty.conf` → `~/.config/kitty/kitty.conf`). Never write directly to `~/.config/<app>/` without a symlink.
